DESCRIPTION:Dara Ó Briain is one of Ireland's most celebrated comedians an
 d broadcasters\, renowned for his razor-sharp wit\, quick-fire improvisatio
 n and ability to turn any audience interaction into comedy gold. After the 
 huge international success of his previous tour\, So\, Where Were We? — w
 hich sold out 173 shows across 20 countries and was named UK Comedy Tour of
  the Year 2023 by Chortle — Dara returns with his new live show\, RE:Crea
 tion. A master storyteller and one of the finest stand-up performers workin
 g today\, Dara's live shows are a thrilling mix of intelligent comedy\, spo
 ntaneous audience interaction and laugh-out-loud storytelling. **Please Not
 e:** Over 16s. Unreserved seating. Tickets are non-refundable except in the
  event of cancellation or postponement.\nMore info: https://comedyatlas.app
